<br>
Plane of Earth A Ring Event. Can be interfered with by Exp'ers, it is requested that non-Raiders leave the zone until it is completed.<br>
<br>
RZ Scripted Event. Non-Raid people are requested to leave the zone. This is a Sony enforcable request.<br>
<br>
Vallon/Tallon as their own scripts, does not affect the rest of the zone, except for the RZ Event, see above.<br>
<br>
Bertox event, Lower CoD. Can be interfered with by Exp'ers in Upper CoD, it is requested that non-Raiders leave the zone until it is completed.<br>
<br>
Caprin Event in Upper CoD. Caprin can be killed and the event blown by a group. The event can be interfered with by exp'ers, so it is requested that non-raides leave the zone until it is completed.<br>
<br>
Aren' Dar just don't XP in the wastes anywhere around the Dragon gate, you might get summoned and killed. Otherwise, PoV zone is not affected.<br>
<br>
Sol Ro, one hour repop on mobs there, Raids in there pretty much eliminate the XP mobs so no point in going if you are flagged.<br>
<br>
Terris Thule, PoNb. PoNb is not an exp zone, this should not be affected.<br>
<br>
Saryn - PoTorment. Not an exp zone, this should not be affected.<br>
<br>
Grummis, does not effect the zone at all<br>
<br>
HoH Trials. Triggers are &quot;A Custodian of Marr&quot; (which is triggered by talking to &quot;Alekson Garn&quot;), &quot;Rhaliq Trell&quot;, and &quot;Tyrdan Faye&quot;. It is requested that exp groups do not kill these mobs, as they are a three day respawn. HoH need not be vacated, but it is requested that exp'rs stay away from the immediate areas of the Raids.<br>
<br>
HoHb Mithanel Marr, not an XP zone so no one bothers, non issue.<br>
<br>
BoT Aangar, Event does not effect the zone, no need to vacate.<br>
<br>
Behemoth in PoI. Only the area in factory should be avoided. The zone need not be vacated.<br>
<br>
Gnome quest and Xanamech in PoI. The gnome is spawned and starts the Xanamech script. This area should be avoided while script is running. The zone need not be vacated.<br>
<br>
The 10th Ring War, Great Divide. This event will despawn the entire zone, folks usually announce before starting it. It is not neccessary to vacate the zone, but it is a courtesy to do so. <br>
<br>
The General in Kithicor for the Roge Epic Script. The zone need not be vacated, but folks are asked to avoid the area.<br>
<br>
Ixblat Fer in Burning Woods for the Cleric Epic. It is just requested to not interfere with this pull.<br>
<br>
Nazok Something-or-other (not sure of the spelling) in Burning Woods for the Cleric Epic. It is just requested to not kill this mob, and to not interfere with this pull.<br>
<br>
Rumblecrush in Umbral Plane. Please don't interfere with the pull of this mob.<br>
<br>
Doomshade in Umbral Plane. This is a minor scripted event. It is requested to not interfere with the pulls involved.<br>
<br>
Gnome quest in Cazic Thule (the zone). Scripted event. Zone need not be vacated.<br>
<br>
Ring Events in Cazic Thule (the zone). There are a few events. Zone need not be vacated.<br>
